 <div class=\"itlv-card\">\n        <div class=\"itlv-card-stars\">\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"itlv-card-text\">Good loafers, fit perfect right away. Leather feels solid. Took 4 days to CA which is pretty fast considering.</p>\n        <p class=\"itlv-card-author\">Michael T.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"itlv-card\">\n        <div class=\"itlv-card-stars\">\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"itlv-card-text\">This dress is even prettier in person! Fits true to size and the fabric is really nice quality. Came super fast, like 3 days</p>\n        <p class=\"itlv-card-author\">Sarah K.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"itlv-card\">\n        <div class=\"itlv-card-stars\">\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star empty\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"itlv-card-text\">Cute flats but they run a little small, had to exchange for half size up. Other than that theyre great and comfy. Shipping took 4 days</p>\n        <p class=\"itlv-card-author\">Emily R.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"itlv-card\">\n        <div class=\"itlv-card-stars\">\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"itlv-card-text\">obsessed with these wedges!! wore them to a wedding and got so many compliments. no blisters either which never happens to me</p>\n        <p class=\"itlv-card-author\">Amanda L.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"itlv-card\">\n        <div class=\"itlv-card-stars\">\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n          <div class=\"itlv-star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z\"/></svg></div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"itlv-card-text\">Needed dress shoes for a wedding, these look great. Real leather not that fake stuff. Got here in 4 day